# ## ğŸ§© Task 1 â€“ Aspect Term Extraction (ATE)

# ### âœ… Objective  
# Extract the **exact spans** (aspect terms) from a sentence that express opinions.

# ### ğŸ§  Model Details  
# - ğŸ§± **Architecture**: Bi-directional GRU / RNN  
# - ğŸ”¤ **Embedding**: GloVe / fastText (pre-trained)  
# - ğŸ·ï¸ **Tagging Scheme**: BIO (Beginning, Inside, Outside)  
# - âŒ **Loss Function**: CrossEntropyLoss (with masking)  
# - ğŸ“Š **Evaluation Metric**: Chunk-level F1 (conlleval)

# ### ğŸ§ª Best Performing Models

# | Model              | Validation F1 |
# |--------------------|---------------|
# | GRU + fastText     | **0.7165**    |
# | GRU + GloVe        | 0.7092        |
# | RNN + fastText     | 0.7013        |
# | RNN + GloVe        | 0.7000        |

# **Test F1 (Best Model â€“ GRU + fastText)**: **0.7132**

# ---

# ## ğŸ’¬ Task 2 â€“ Aspect Sentiment Classification (ASC)

# ### âœ… Objective  
# For each extracted aspect term, predict its **sentiment label**.

# ### ğŸ§  Model Details  
# - ğŸ§± **Architecture**: Bi-LSTM with Aspect-Specific Attention  
# - ğŸ”¤ **Embedding**: GloVe (300D)  
# - ğŸ§  **Input**: Context tokens + aspect term index  
# - ğŸ¯ **Attention**: Focuses on relevant context around aspect  
# - âŒ **Loss Function**: CrossEntropyLoss  
# - ğŸ“Š **Evaluation Metric**: Accuracy

# ### ğŸ† Best Results

# | Metric                     | Score     |
# |----------------------------|-----------|
# | Validation Accuracy        | **0.6523** |
# | Test Accuracy (Best Model) | **0.6250** |

